bbcode_enabled = true
text = "[center][color=#D9C080][font_size=28]You traveled far to get here... looking for [color=#A6872A]gold and glory[/color].

A tip you got told you that in the middle of the desert, lay a tomb, where a lavish emperor of old lay with his mortal possessions.

Rumors say that some have tried to claim this treasure for themselves. Not sure what happened to them, but some say they [color=#8B3A3A]went mad[/color].

But you have nothing to lose.

With your shovel, lamp, and a couple bullets in your pocket, you descend to the depths below.[/font_size][/color][/center]"
